description: It’s hard to know what the next job will bring: Clay, sand or something in between? Will it require traditional compacting methods or will you have to adjust amplitude and frequency because of sensitive surroundings? Either way you will need a roller that produces. Ammann Soil Compactors provide industry-leading compaction outputs – whatever the application. Your job-site conditions might change, but you will always have a need for productivity and performance.
name: Single Drum Rollers
